==Other Asian religions== ===Buddhism=== {{Main article|Chinese Buddhism|Tibetan Buddhism}} The region is home to [[Chinese Buddhism|Chinese Buddhist schools and traditions]] and [[Tibetan Buddhism|Tibetan Buddhist]] traditions, which are popular among [[Mongols in China|Mongols]] as well as increasingly among [[Manchu people|Manchus]] and [[Han Chinese]]. The [[Jile Temple]] is an important Chinese Buddhist centre in [[Harbin]]. {{multiple image | align = center | direction = horizontal | width = 150
