===Islam=== [[File:HRBmosque.JPG|thumb|150px|The [[Daowai Mosque]] in [[Harbin]].]] Northeast China is home to a small number of [[Hui people|Hui Chinese]] who traditionally follow [[Islam]]. As of 2010 there are 52,100 Muslims in the region, equal to 0.04% of the total population.<ref name="2010-Islam"/> {{clear}}
